# 🌙 Nurul Islam  
A website dedicated to sharing Islamic knowledge, including **Quran & Hadith**, **prayer times**, **Islamic articles**, and **lectures**.

## 📖 About the Website  
**Nurul Islam** aims to provide authentic Islamic knowledge in an easy-to-access format. The website includes:  

- 📝 **Islamic Articles** – Covering various topics on faith, history, and daily life.  
- 📜 **Quran & Hadith** – Read and reflect on divine guidance.  
- 🕋 **Prayer Times** – Stay updated on daily Salah timings.  
- 🎥 **Islamic Videos & Lectures** – Learn from scholars and speakers.  
- 📩 **Contact Page** – Reach out for inquiries or feedback.  

## 🚀 Hosting  
This website is hosted using **GitHub Pages**.  

## 🔗 Visit the Website  
[Click here to access Nurul Islam](https://yourusername.github.io/nurul-islam/)  

